com.oym.indoor

Class IBeacon

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oym.indoor.IBeacon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<IBeacon>

    public class IBeacon
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<IBeacon>
    This class includes all the information regarding the iBeacon Items stored in Links.
